  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered code generation with conversational interface",
    "Real-time Next.js application development in E2B sandboxes",
    "Multi-framework support (Next.js, Angular, React, Vue, Svelte)",
    "Live preview with split-pane interface and syntax highlighting",
    "File explorer with code editing capabilities",
    "Smart usage tracking with credit system and rate limiting",
    "Subscription management with Polar.sh integration",
    "OAuth integrations (Figma, GitHub) for importing designs and repositories",
    "Background job processing with Inngest and Agent Kit",
    "Real-time database with Convex for instant updates"
